The present Supreme Court should go down in history as "the salami court." 
</P>
<P>
It has taken several slices off civil rights. Now, in the CNN case, it's 
freedom of the press. What's next? 
</P>
<P>
FREDERIC E. PAMP 
</P>
<P>
Santa Ynez 
</P>
