<HEADLINE>
<P>
FANS WILL FIGHT ON ABOUT TROJANS LOSING TO NOTRE DAME AGAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
After suffering through another USC loss to an overrated Notre Dame team, I 
have come to the belief that Larry Smith is a Big Ten coach masquerading as a 
Pac-10 coach. 
</P>
<P>
I question a game plan that does not attack the most vulnerable part of a 
defense. The weakest link of the Irish defense is the secondary. So what 
happens? Not one deep pass. 
</P>
<P>
