<DOCID> 315931 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 1, 1990, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
