<TEXT>
<P>
Helen Dettweiler, 74, first woman golfer to turn pro. Miss Dettweiler, who 
maintained residences in Portland, Ore., and Palm Desert in her later years, 
was one of 12 charter members of the Ladies Professional Golf Assn. in 1950. 
</P>
<P>
