FORCES -- KUWAIT; BUSH, GEORGE; HUSSEIN, SADDAM; DIPLOMACY; UNITED STATES -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN POLICY; BAKER, JAMES A III; 
AZIZ, TARIK; CONGRESS (U.S.); UNITED STATES -- POLITICS; UNITED STATES -- 
GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS 
</P>
